Setting Parameters

snow %>% 
  select(Latitude, Longitude) %>% 
  summary()

##  1st Qu.:39.56   1st Qu.:-122.2  
##  Median :41.85   Median :-122.1  
##  Mean   :47.36   Mean   :-124.3  
##  3rd Qu.:52.62   3rd Qu.:-121.8  
##  Max.   :70.49   Max.   :-110.2
lat <- c(39.20, 70.49)
long <- c(-160.6, -110.2)
bbox <- make_bbox(long, lat, f = 0.05)

Getting a Base Map

b <- get_map(bbox, maptype = "terrain", source = "stamen")
ggmap(b)
